SUMMARY:Motor Town: Behind The Wheel | Ep. 17 - This Looked Like a Short
 Drive on the Map
DESCRIPTION:A relaxing drive turns into an unexpected journey. Roads will
 be missed, schedules will be ignored, and vibes will remain immaculate.
 Enjoy realistic driving in the open world. Relaxing cargo deliveries or
 driving buses and taxis will give you enough money to buy new cars and
 parts. You can test your driving skills at the race track. It's all about
 pure driving pleasure!
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=71xDKKhBhpA
CATEGORIES:Motor Town: Behind The Wheel
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
