LAST-MODIFIED:20260214T171000Z
DTSTART:20260211T213000Z
DTEND:20260211T233000Z
SUMMARY:World of Warships | Ep. 5 - The Ocean Is My Enemy Now
DESCRIPTION:Strategic naval combat, careful positioning, and the sea
 personally deciding I've had enough success for one lifetime. Immerse
 yourself in thrilling naval battles and assemble an armada of over 400
 ships from the first half of the 20th century - from stealthy destroyers
 to gigantic battleships. Change the look of your ship, choose upgrades to
 suit your play style, and go into battle with other players!
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kZh3O5PVUM0
CATEGORIES:World of Warships
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
