SUMMARY:Simon the Sorcerer Origins | Ep. 5 - Trying Every Item on
 Everything, Calmly
DESCRIPTION:Peak adventure-game logic. The solution is obvious... once
 you've tried absolutely everything else first. Experience the Magical
 World like never before in Simon the Sorcerer Origins, the highly
 anticipated prequel to the cult classic Point-and-Click adventure series.
 In this new adventure, Simon, the most sarcastic wizard in video game
 history, returns to reveal secrets and stories from his past!
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rYUMm2ktOAY
CATEGORIES:Simon the Sorcerer Origins
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
